  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220663806079\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220663806079\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">어제는 수요일</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">오후진료 3시까지 하는 날이었다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">진료가 끝나고 원장님께 교육을 받고</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">회식을 하러갔다</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">회식의 주제는 우리 새로오신 새희샘의 환영식 겸 더 밝은 2016년 위한 화이팅? ㅋㅋㅋ&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">회식 장소는 근처에 있는 전라도식 계절음식 전문점 \"<b>마실</b>\"로 갔다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">가끔 지나가면서..</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">'언제 한번 꼭 가봐야지' 했는데 어제 우리 병원식구들이랑 다녀왔어요 ^^</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">들어가기 전 입구에 있는 배너를 보니..</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">먹고 싶은 메뉴가 많네요&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">(제가 배가 많이 고팠나봐요 ㅡㅡ;;)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_286/isuhani_1458780357360vGXHw_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093908960.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"640\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:640px;\" id=\"20160324_286/isuhani_1458780357360vGXHw_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093908960.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_286/isuhani_1458780357360vGXHw_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093908960.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">입구도 깔끔하구~</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_236/isuhani_1458780357570szGxA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093909412.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"20160324_236/isuhani_1458780357570szGxA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093909412.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_236/isuhani_1458780357570szGxA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093909412.jpg?type=w3\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_42/isuhani_1458780357713CJ43s_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093909830.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"20160324_42/isuhani_1458780357713CJ43s_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093909830.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_42/isuhani_1458780357713CJ43s_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093909830.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">식당 내부도 넓고 깨끗하고 좋았어요</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">테이블에 앉아서 먹을수도 있는데,&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">우리는 식사하면서 이런저런 이야기도 해야해서 조용한 방으로 들어갔답니다</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_293/isuhani_1458780357862GXIss_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093910048.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"20160324_293/isuhani_1458780357862GXIss_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093910048.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_293/isuhani_1458780357862GXIss_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093910048.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">자 그럼.. 배가 고프니깐 얼른 주문을 해볼까요</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">모듬<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">회. 아구찜. 두부김치두루치기를 시켰는데..</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">밑반찬 많이 나오네요~</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_185/isuhani_1458780358766llCju_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093911402.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:270px;\" id=\"20160324_185/isuhani_1458780358766llCju_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093911402.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_185/isuhani_1458780358766llCju_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093911402.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">반찬도 맛있고&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">첫 메뉴는 모듬회</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_59/isuhani_1458780359130EnJle_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093911972.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"853\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:480px; rheight:853px;\" id=\"20160324_59/isuhani_1458780359130EnJle_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093911972.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_59/isuhani_1458780359130EnJle_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093911972.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_218/isuhani_1458780359267U59t5_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093912482.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"20160324_218/isuhani_1458780359267U59t5_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093912482.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_218/isuhani_1458780359267U59t5_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093912482.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">초장에 찍어서 한점</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">맛있겠쥬?</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/moon_and_james/original_9.png?type=p50_50\" alt=\"moon_and_james-9\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">두번째 메뉴: 두부김치두루치기</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_235/isuhani_1458780359436IJakD_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093912837.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"20160324_235/isuhani_1458780359436IJakD_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093912837.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_235/isuhani_1458780359436IJakD_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093912837.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">세번째 메뉴: 아구찜</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_8/isuhani_1458780359603EW4rS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093913201.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"20160324_8/isuhani_1458780359603EW4rS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093913201.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_8/isuhani_1458780359603EW4rS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093913201.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">콩나물만 잔뜩이네ㅡㅡ;;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">아구는 안에 숨어있다&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">ㅋㅋ&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">나중에 나원장님도 오셔서&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">꼬막찜 하나 추가했는데</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_101/isuhani_1458780360237v80hA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093914605.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:480px;\" id=\"20160324_101/isuhani_1458780360237v80hA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093914605.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_101/isuhani_1458780360237v80hA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093914605.jpg?type=w3\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">너무 맛있었어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">꼬막사랑&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">ㅎㅎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">전라도식이라 그런가..&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">입에 잘 맞았나 너무 맛있게 잘먹었다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">식사가 끝나고 둘러보는데</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">벽에 요게 붙어있드라고요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">그래서 읽어봤는데..</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_270/isuhani_1458780359754lHWuI_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093913514.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"640\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:640px;\" id=\"20160324_270/isuhani_1458780359754lHWuI_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093913514.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336096787F')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160324_270/isuhani_1458780359754lHWuI_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160324_093913514.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">태그해야지!</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/moon_and_james/o